quran[118]{c,v,t}:
  23,1,"Mu by’ukuri, abemeramana baratsinze"
  23,2,Babandi bakora amasengesho yabo bibombaritse
  23,3,Na babandi birengagiza ibidafite akamaro (mu mvugo no mu bikorwa)
  23,4,Na babandi batanga
  23,5,Na babandi barinda ibitsina byabo (ntibishobore mu busambanyi)
  23,6,"Uretse gusa kubagore babo cyangwaku bo bafiteho ububasha (abaja)86, kuko kuri bo batabigayirwa"
  23,7,"Ariko abazashaka (kwinezeza) ku batari abo (bavuzwe), rwose abo bazaba batandukiriye"
  23,8,Na babandi barinda ibyo baragijwe kandi bakubahirizaamasezerano
  23,9,"Na babandi bahozaho amasengesho (y’itegeko, bakayakorera ku bihe byagenwe)"
  23,10,Abo ni bo bazungura
  23,11,"Bazazungura Firidawusi (Ijuru risumba ayandi), bakazaribamo ubuziraherezo"
  23,12,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, twaremye umuntu (Adamu) tumukomoye mu ibumba ry’umwimerere"
  23,13,Maze tumuha kororoka (kw’abamukomokaho) binyuzemu ntanga (twashyize) mu cyicaro gitekanye (nyababyeyi)
  23,14,"Hanyuma intanga (tuyiremamo) urusoro rw’amaraso, hanyuma (tururemamo) ikinyama, muri icyo kinyama turemamo amagufa, maze amagufa tuyambika umubiri, hanyuma (duhuhamo roho) tugihindura ikindi kiremwa (kigaragaza ishusho). Bityo, ubutagatifu ni ubwa Allah, Umuremyi uhebuje"
  23,15,"Nyuma y’ibyo, mu by’ukuri, muzapfa"
  23,16,"Hanyuma (nanone), muzazurwa ku munsi w’imperuka"
  23,17,"Rwose twaremye ibirere birindwi (tubishyira) hejuru yanyu, kandi ntabwo twirengagiza cyangwa ngo turangarane ibiremwa (byacu)"
  23,18,"Twanamanuye amazi (imvura) mu kirere ku rugero rukwiye, tuyagumisha mu butaka, kandi mu by’ukuri, dushoboye no kuyakamya"
  23,19,"Muri ayo mazi, tuyaberezamo imirima y’imitende n’imizabibu, musangamo imbuto nyinshi, ndetse hakanabamo izo murya"
  23,20,"(Muri ayo mazi kandi Allah yabamerejemo) igiti (cy’umuzeti) cyera (mu kibaya) cy’Umusozi wa Sinayi, kivamo amavuta yifashishwa n’abayafungura"
  23,21,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, mu matungo (iremwa ryayo) harimo inyigisho kuri mwe (zigaragaza ubushobozi bwa Allah). Tubahamo ibyo munywa (amata) biturutse mu nda zayo, kandi (ayo matungo) muyakuramo byinshi bibafitiye akamaro, ndetse amwe muri yo muranayarya"
  23,22,Kandi (ayo matungo) ndetse n’amato birabatwara (iyo muri mu ngendo zanyu)
  23,23,"Rwose, twohereje Nuhu ku bantu be, maze arababwira ati \"Yemwe bantu banjye! Nimugaragire Allah. Nta yindi mana mufite itari we (Allah).Ese ntimutinya (ibihano bye)"
  23,24,"Ariko abanyacyubahiro bo mu bantu be bahakanye, baravuga bati \"Uyu ntacyo ari cyo usibye kuba ari umuntu nkamwe, icyo ashaka ni ukwishyira hejuru (ngo abategeke). Kandi iyo Allahaza gushaka (kohereza intumwa) yari kohereza Malayika. Ntabwo twigeze twumva ibintu nk’ibi ku babyeyi bacu bo hambere"
  23,25,"Mu by’ukuri ni umuntu wahanzweho n’amashitani. Bityo, nimutegereze igihe runaka (agarure ubwenge maze areke ibyo avuga cyangwa apfe mumukire)"
  23,26,"(Nuhu) aravuga ati \"Nyagasani wanjye! Ntabara unkize (abantu banjye) kubera kobahakana (ibyo mvuga)"
  23,27,"Nuko tumuhishurira tugira tuti \"Ubaka inkuge tukugenzura, (bijyanye) n’ubutumwa bwacu. Maze itegeko ryacu (ryo kubarimbura) nirisohora, nuko itanura rigapfupfunyukamo amazi afite imbaraga (nk’ikimenyetso cy’uko ibihano bije), uzinjizemo ikigabo n’ikigore (kuri buri bwoko bw’inyamaswa), ndetse n’umuryango wawe, usibye abaciriweho iteka muri wo (ari bo umugore wawe n’umwana wawe)\". Kandi ntugire icyo umbaza (uvuganira) inkozi z’ibibi. Mu by’ukuri,bo bagomba kurohama"
  23,28,"Maze wowe n’abo muri kumwe mu nkuge nimumara gutuza, uzavuge uti \"Ishimwe n’ikuzo byuzuye ni ibya Allah, we waturokoye abantu b’abahakanyi"
  23,29,"Uzanavuge uti \"Nyagasani wanjye! Nyorohereza umpe kururukira ahuje imigisha, kuko ari wowe uhebuje mu kururutsa (abantu mu mahoro)"
  23,30,"Mu by’ukuri, muri ibyo (kurokora abemeye no kurimbura abahakanye) harimo ibimenyetso (bigaragaza ubushobozi bwa Allah). Kandi mu by’ukuri, tugerageza (abantu)"
  23,31,Nuko nyuma yabo turema ikindi gisekuru (aba Adi bo ku bwa Hudu)
  23,32,"Maze tuboherereza intumwa (Hudu) ibakomokamo (ibabwira iti) \"Nimugaragire Allah, nta yindi mana mufite itari we. Ese ntimutinya (ibihano bye)"
  23,33,"Maze abanyacyubahiro mu bantu be bahakanye (Allah) bakanahinyura kuzahura n’umunsi w’imperuka, kandi twarabahaye ubuzima bwiza hano ku isi, (baravuga bati) \"Uyu nta cyo ari cyo usibye kuba ari umuntu nkamwe, urya ibyo murya akananywa ibyo munywa"
  23,34,"Kandi nimuramuka mwumviye umuntu nka mwe,mu by’ukuri, muzaba mubaye abanyagihombo"
  23,35,Ese abasezeranya ko nimuramuka mupfuye mugahinduka igitaka ndetse n’amagufa (akabora) muzazurwa
  23,36,"Ibyo musezeranywa (na Hudu) biri kure, kure cyane"
  23,37,"Nta bundi (buzima buzabaho), usibye ubu buzima bwacu bwo ku isi! Turapfa, tukanabaho (hakaza abandi) kandi ntabwo tuzazurwa"
  23,38,"(Hudu) nta cyo ari cyo, usibye kuba ari umuntu uhimbira Allah ibinyoma, kandi ntabwo tuzamwemera"
  23,39,"(Hudu) aravuga ati \"Nyagasani wanjye! Ntabara unkize (abantu banjye) kubera kobahakana (ibyo mvuga)"
  23,40,"(Allah) aravuga ati \"Rwose mu kanya gato baraba bicuza (impamvu bahakanye)"
  23,41,"Maze urusaku rw’ibihano rubatera rutabarenganyije, nuko tubahindura nk’ibishingwe (bireremba hejuru y’amazi). Bityo, kurimbuka ni kube ku bahakanyi"
  23,42,Nuko nyuma yabo turema ibindi bisekuru
  23,43,Nta bantu bashobora kwihutisha igihe cyabo (cyo kurimbuka) cyangwa ngo bagikerereze
  23,44,"Hanyuma twohereza intumwa zacu zigenda zikurikirana, ariko buri uko intumwa yageraga mu bantu bayo (yatumweho) barayihinyuraga. Nuko tugenda tubakurikiza (ibihano) bamwe ku bandi, kandi tubagira iciro ry’imigani (kugira ngo bizabere isomo n’inyigisho ku bazabaho nyuma). Bityo, kurimbuka ni kube ku bantu batemera"
  23,45,"Hanyuma twoherezaMusa n’umuvandimwe we Haruna, tubahayeibitangaza byacu n’ibimenyetso bigaragara"
  23,46,"(Tubohereza) kwa Farawo n’ibyegera bye, ariko (barabasuzugura) bagaragaza ubwibone, kandi bari abantu bishyira hejuru"
  23,47,"Baravuga bati \"Ese twemere abantu babiri bameze nka twe, kandi abantu babo ari abacakara bacu"
  23,48,"Nuko babahinyura bombi, maze (Farawo n’ibyegera bye) baba mu boretswe"
  23,49,Kandi rwose twahaye Musa igitabo (Tawurati) kugira ngo bayoboke
  23,50,"Twanagize mwene Mariyamu (Issa)na nyina, ikimenyetso (kigaragaza ubushobozi bwacu), nuko tubatuza ahirengeye, hatekanye kandi hari amazi"
  23,51,"Yemwe ntumwa! Nimurye amafunguro meza (aziruwe) kandi mukore ibikorwa byiza. Mu by’ukuri, njye ndi Umumenyi uhebuje w’ibyo mukora"
  23,52,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, uyu muryango wanyu (idini rya Islam) ni umuryango umwe, nanjye nkaba Nyagasani wanyu; bityo nimuntinye (mwubahiriza ibyo nabategetse)"
  23,53,"Ariko idini ryabo bariciyemo ibice, buri gatsiko kishimira ibyako"
  23,54,"Bityo (yewe Muhamadi), barekere mu buyobe bwabo kugeza igihe runaka (bazagerwaho n’ibihano)"
  23,55,Ese bakeka ko imitungo n’urubyaro tubaha (ku isi)
  23,56,Tubibihutishiriza ku bw’ineza (bakwiye)? (Siko bimeze) ahubwo (ni ukubareshya) nyamara ntibabimenya
  23,57,"Mu by’ukuri, babandi bitwararika kubera gutinya Nyagasani wabo"
  23,58,Na babandi bemera ibimenyetso bya Nyagasani wabo
  23,59,Na babandi batagira icyo babangikanya na Nyagasani wabo
  23,60,"Ndetse na babandi batanga (amaturo) mu byo bahawe, imitima yabo ifite ubwoba kuko (batekereza ko) bazasubira kwa Nyagasani wabo"
  23,61,"Abo ni bo bihutira gukora ibyiza,kandi ni na bo baza imbere muri byo"
  23,62,"Kandi ntawe dutegeka gukora icyo adashoboye, ndetse dufite igitabo kivuga ukuri (cyanditsemo ibikorwa byabo), kandi ntibazarenganywa"
  23,63,"Ahubwo imitima yabo iri mu bujiji (bwo kudasobanukirwa) iyi (Qur’an), ndetse hari n’ibindi bikorwa (bibi) bakora bitari ibyo"
  23,64,"Kugeza ubwo duhannye abakungu muri bo, bagatangira guca bugufi batabaza"
  23,65,"Mwitabaza kuri uyu munsi! Mu by’ukuri, ntitubatabara"
  23,66,Rwose mwajyaga musomerwa amagambo yanjye ariko mukayatera umugongo
  23,67,"(Muvugako Umusigiti Mutagatifu wa Maka ari uwanyu ntawawubakuramo) mukawiratana, naho nijoro mukarara muvuga nabi (iyi Qur’an)"
  23,68,"Ese ntibatekereza ku magambo (ya Allah), cyangwa (babuzwa kuyemera nuko) bagezweho n’ibitarageze ku babyeyi babo bo hambere"
  23,69,"Cyangwa (babuzwa kuyoboka) no kuba bataramenye Intumwa yabo (Muhamadi), bikaba ari byo bituma bayihakana"
  23,70,"Cyangwa bavuga ko (Muhamadi) yahanzweho n’amashitani? (Siko bimeze), ahubwo yabazaniye ukuri (idini ya Isilamu) ariko abenshi muri bo banga ukuri"
  23,71,"Kandi iyo ukuri kuza kuba kujyanye n’ibyifuzo byabo, rwose ibirere n’isi ndetse n’ibibirimo byari kwangirika. Nyamara twabazaniye urwibutso rwabo (Qur’an), ariko barutera umugongo"
  23,72,"Cyangwa (babuzwa kwemera) no kuba waba ubasaba igihembo (kugira ngo ubagezeho ubutumwa)? (Siko bimeze!) Ahubwo, ibihembo byaNyagasani wawe nibyo byiza, kandi ni we uhebuje mu batanga amafunguro"
  23,73,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, ubahamagarira kugana inzira igororotse"
  23,74,Kandi rwose babandi batemera umunsi w’imperukabayobye cyane iyo nzira
  23,75,"N’iyo tuza kubagirira impuhwe tukabakuriraho ingorane barimo, bari gukomeza gutsimbarara ku bwigomeke bwabo, barindagira"
  23,76,"Kandi rwose twabahaye ibihano ariko ntibaca bugufi kuri Nyagasani wabo, ndetse ntibanamusaba bibombaritse"
  23,77,"Kugeza ubwo (ku munsi w’imperuka) tuzabafungurira umuryango w’ibihano bikaze, maze bakazabibamo bihebye"
  23,78,"Kandi (Allah) ni we wabahaye ukumva, ukubona ndetse (abaha) n’imitima (kugira ngo musobanukirwe), ariko ni gake mushimira"
  23,79,"Ni na we wabakwirakwije ku isi, kandi iwe ni ho muzakoranyirizwa"
  23,80,"Kandi ni we utanga ubuzima akanatanga n’urupfu, ndetse ni na we ugenga ukubisikana kw’ijoro n’amanywa. Ese ntimugira ubwenge"
  23,81,Ahubwo bavuga nk’ibyo abo hambere bavugaga
  23,82,"Baravuze bati \"Ese nidupfa, tugahinduka igitaka ndetse n’amagufa (akabora), koko tuzazurwa"
  23,83,"Rwose ibyo twabisezeranyijwe mbere, twe n’ababyeyi bacu. Ibi nta kindi biri cyo usibye kuba ari inkuru z’abo hambere"
  23,84,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Ese isi n’ibiyirimo ni ibya nde niba mubizi"
  23,85,"Bazavuga bati \"Niibya Allah\". Vuga uti \"Nonese ubwo ntimwibuka"
  23,86,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Ni nde Nyagasani w’ibirere birindwi, ndetse ni na nde Nyagasani w’intebe y’ubwami ihambaye (Arshi)"
  23,87,"Bazavuga bati \"Ni ibya Allah\".Vuga uti \"Nonese ubwo ntimutinya"
  23,88,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Ni nde ufite ubwami bwa buri kintu mu kuboko kwe, akaba ari nawe urinda (umwikinzeho) mu gihe ntawarinda (uwo yageneye ibihano), niba mubizi"
  23,89,"Bazavuga bati \"Ni ibya Allah\".Vuga uti \"Nonese ni gute mushukwa (mugateshuka ku kuri)"
  23,90,"Ahubwo twabazaniye ukuri, ariko mu by’ukuri (ababangikanyamana) ni abanyabinyoma"
  23,91,"Ntabwo Allahagira umwana kandi nta yindi manaabangikanye nawe. (Iyo haza kubaho imana nyinshi), buri mana yari kwiharira ibyo yaremye, kandi zimwe zari kuganza izindi. Ubutagatifu ni ubwa Allah kandi ntaho ahuriye n’ibyo bamubangikanya nabyo"
  23,92,Ni Umumenyi w’ibitagaragara n’ibigaragara! Ntaho ahuriye n’ibyo bamubangikanya nabyo
  23,93,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti\"Nyagasani wanjye!Ni biba ngombwa ko unyereka ibyo (bihano) basezeranyijwe"
  23,94,Nyagasani wanjye! Ntuzanshyire mu bantu b’ababangikanyamana
  23,95,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, kukwereka ibyo twabasezeranyije turabishoboye"
  23,96,Jya ukumira ikibi ukoresheshe icyiza. Twe tuzi neza ibyo bavuga
  23,97,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Nyagasani wanjye! Nkwikinzeho ngo undinde ibishuko by’amashitani"
  23,98,Nanakwikinzeho Nyagasani wanjye! Ngo uyandinde ntanyegere
  23,99,"(Bazakomeza guhakana) kugeza ubwo umwe muri bo agezweho n’urupfu, maze akavuga ati \"Nyagasani wanjye!Ngarura (ku isi)"
  23,100,"Kugira ngo mbashe gukora ibyiza ntakoze. Ibyo ntibishoboka! Mu by’ukuri, ibyo ni amagambo yivugira, kandi inyuma yabo hari urusika (rubabuza kugaruka ku isi) kuzageza ku munsi bazazurirwaho"
  23,101,"Hanyuma impanda nivuzwa, nta masano azarangwa hagati yabo kuri uwo munsi, ndetse nta n’uzaba yitaye ku wundi"
  23,102,"Bityo, ab’iminzani yabo (y’ibikorwa by’iza) izaremera; abo ni bo bakiranutsi"
  23,103,"Naho ab’iminzani yabo (y’ibikorwa byiza) izagira uburemere buke; abo ni bo bazaba barihemukiye, bazaba mu muriro wa Jahanamu ubuziraherezo"
  23,104,"Umuriro uzatwika uburanga bwabo (iminwa iveho), maze bawubemo bashinyitse"
  23,105,"(Babwirwe bati) \"Ese ntimwajyaga musomerwa amagambo yanjye mazemukayahinyura"
  23,106,"Bazavuga bati \"Nyagasani wacu! Twaganjijwe n’irari ryacu maze tuba mu bantu bayobye"
  23,107,"Nyagasani wacu!Wudukuremo (udusubize ku isi). Nituramuka dusubiye (mu buyobe), mu by’ukuri,tuzaba turi inkozi z’ibibi"
  23,108,"(Allah) avuge ati \"Nimuwubemo (musuzuguritse) kandi ntimugire icyo mwongera kumbwira"
  23,109,"Mu by’ukuri, hari itsinda mu bagaragu banjye (ryajyaga risaba Allah) rigira riti \"Nyagasani wacu! Twaremeye, bityo tubabarire unatugirire impuhwe, kuko ari wowe uhebuje abandi mu kugira impuhwe"
  23,110,"Ariko mwarabasuzuguraga kugeza ubwo babibagije kunyibuka, kandi mwajyaga mubaseka"
  23,111,"Mu by’ukuri, uyu munsi mbahembye (Ijuru) kubera kwihangana kwabo, ndetse ni nabo batsinze"
  23,112,"(Allah) azabwira (inkozi z’ibibi) ati \"Ese mwamaze imyaka ingahe ku isi"
  23,113,"Bazavuga bati \"Twahamaze umunsi cyangwaigice cy’umunsi. Ngaho baza abazi kubara"
  23,114,"(Allah) avuge ati \"Mwamaze igihe gito cyane. Iyaba mwari muzi (ko igihe mugiye kumara ari cyo kirekire kuruta icyo mwamaze ku isi, muba mwaremeye)"
  23,115,"Ese mukeka ko twabaremye dukina (nta mpamvu), kandi ko mutazagarurwa iwacu"
  23,116,"Bityo, Allah asumba byose, Umwami w’ukuri; nta yindi mana ikwiye gusengwa by’ukuri uretse we, Nyagasani w’intebe y’icyubahiro"
  23,117,"N’uzabangikanya Allah n’ikindi kintu adafitiye gihamya, rwose ibarura rye rizakorwa na Nyagasani we. Mu by’ukuri, abahakanyi ntibazatsinda"
  23,118,"Unavuge (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Nyagasani wanjye! Babarira unagire impuhwe, kuko ari wowe uhebuje abandi mu kugira impuhwe"